1
00:00:09,114 --> 00:00:13,160
♪I defy heaven, fate,
and so-called immortality♪

2
00:00:13,160 --> 00:00:17,800
♪At last you say
we've been apart too long♪

3
00:00:17,800 --> 00:00:22,840
♪Unwilling, unyielding, I won't let go♪

4
00:00:22,840 --> 00:00:28,000
♪With you, even a dried sea
learns to embrace a stream♪

5
00:00:28,000 --> 00:00:32,415
♪If heaven divides us, I'll reunite us,
with love as our vessel♪

6
00:00:32,415 --> 00:00:37,167
♪If it forbids it, I'll shatter
the absurd Heavenly Dao♪

7
00:00:37,167 --> 00:00:42,400
♪Even if countless stars
turn into my foes♪

8
00:00:42,400 --> 00:00:47,853
♪To grow old with you, we burn
through the end of the long night♪

9
00:00:50,820 --> 00:00:55,760
=Rise Again=

10
00:00:56,144 --> 00:00:58,878
=Episode 7=

11
00:01:20,560 --> 00:01:22,599
This is the Heavenly Yin Cold Marrow.

12
00:01:34,400 --> 00:01:35,000
You.

13
00:01:35,439 --> 00:01:35,920
I...

14
00:01:40,640 --> 00:01:41,719
Why does it not hurt anymore?

15
00:02:16,800 --> 00:02:19,439
Many thanks for saving Xiaonuan.

16
00:02:19,560 --> 00:02:19,879
I...

17
00:02:19,879 --> 00:02:20,719
Grandpa, get up.

18
00:02:21,000 --> 00:02:22,080
Why bow to him?

19
00:02:22,400 --> 00:02:22,960
Get up.

20
00:02:23,400 --> 00:02:24,639
Come on, get up.

21
00:02:25,479 --> 00:02:26,639
Don't keep bowing to me.

22
00:02:28,080 --> 00:02:29,719
Since Xiaonuan is your granddaughter,

23
00:02:30,000 --> 00:02:31,080
it was only natural to save her.

24
00:02:32,479 --> 00:02:35,039
Grandpa, he cured my cold poison,

25
00:02:35,439 --> 00:02:37,520
and we're even now.

26
00:02:37,800 --> 00:02:39,319
After all, I cured his mom's illness.

27
00:02:39,319 --> 00:02:40,080
Xiaonuan!

28
00:02:42,039 --> 00:02:43,400
Ye Xiaonuan is right.

29
00:02:43,599 --> 00:02:46,080
She really cured my mom.

30
00:02:47,439 --> 00:02:51,159
Never expected you two
to have such a fate.

31
00:02:52,439 --> 00:02:54,319
You flatter me. As for fate...

32
00:02:55,759 --> 00:02:56,840
that's a stretch.

33
00:02:58,199 --> 00:02:58,879
Dr. Ye,

34
00:02:59,439 --> 00:03:00,639
your outfit today makes you

35
00:03:01,159 --> 00:03:02,120
a different person.

36
00:03:06,599 --> 00:03:08,719
At the hospital, I'm a doctor.

37
00:03:09,280 --> 00:03:10,439
After work, I'm just myself.

38
00:03:11,080 --> 00:03:11,759
What's wrong?

39
00:03:14,800 --> 00:03:17,639
I will continue treating you.

40
00:03:18,800 --> 00:03:20,479
You still have a long life ahead of you.

41
00:03:20,960 --> 00:03:22,039
Just be yourself.

42
00:03:25,919 --> 00:03:26,879
Is that true?

43
00:03:30,439 --> 00:03:30,879
Of course.

44
00:03:31,919 --> 00:03:32,639
That's good.

45
00:03:34,719 --> 00:03:35,400
I didn't expect you

46
00:03:36,159 --> 00:03:37,280
to have this side.

47
00:03:38,919 --> 00:03:39,759
Are you surprised?

48
00:03:43,719 --> 00:03:45,439
Don't tell me you like me
dressed like this?

49
00:03:48,360 --> 00:03:49,360
Just kidding.

50
00:03:49,360 --> 00:03:50,560
Don't be so serious.

51
00:03:51,120 --> 00:03:52,120
You've got

52
00:03:52,439 --> 00:03:54,639
the same temper Tianmiao had as a kid.

53
00:03:55,759 --> 00:03:57,560
What's your connection with my grandpa?

54
00:04:02,319 --> 00:04:03,639
If you don't want to say it, forget it.

55
00:04:06,080 --> 00:04:07,159
For the future treatment...

56
00:04:08,199 --> 00:04:09,439
will it always be like last night?

57
00:04:13,599 --> 00:04:15,080
I don't understand a pure yin body.

58
00:04:15,680 --> 00:04:16,560
I only know

59
00:04:16,959 --> 00:04:18,199
that this illness can't be cured.

60
00:04:19,439 --> 00:04:20,639
My granddad told me

61
00:04:21,639 --> 00:04:23,199
when my cold poison flares up,

62
00:04:23,639 --> 00:04:24,720
I only have five years left.

63
00:04:27,040 --> 00:04:28,319
That's why you live like this...

64
00:04:29,759 --> 00:04:30,959
Carpe diem,

65
00:04:31,199 --> 00:04:32,319
and enjoy the moment.

66
00:04:33,560 --> 00:04:34,360
Exactly.

67
00:04:35,480 --> 00:04:37,399
So you can fully cure me?

68
00:04:37,600 --> 00:04:38,399
Yes.

69
00:04:39,040 --> 00:04:40,199
Of course I can.

70
00:04:41,199 --> 00:04:42,759
But every treatment

71
00:04:43,680 --> 00:04:45,160
will be just like last night.

72
00:04:46,800 --> 00:04:48,199
You've already seen everything.

73
00:04:48,800 --> 00:04:49,600
So what?

74
00:04:52,279 --> 00:04:52,959
By the way,

75
00:04:54,319 --> 00:04:55,560
if you've made up your mind,

76
00:04:55,680 --> 00:04:56,600
come find me.

77
00:04:57,839 --> 00:05:00,160
What happened last night...

78
00:05:00,480 --> 00:05:02,160
you're not to tell a soul.

79
00:05:07,160 --> 00:05:07,959
Su Wubing,

80
00:05:09,399 --> 00:05:10,560
I owe you a favor.

81
00:05:22,680 --> 00:05:24,160
You don't owe me anything.

82
00:05:27,300 --> 00:05:28,800
You see?

83
00:05:28,800 --> 00:05:32,080
Putting her in charge just doesn't work.

84
00:05:35,279 --> 00:05:36,879
We thought you wouldn't dare come back.

85
00:05:40,519 --> 00:05:41,319
What?

86
00:05:42,800 --> 00:05:44,639
It's rare to see you all so formal.

87
00:05:45,160 --> 00:05:47,120
This is my own company's board meeting.

88
00:05:47,279 --> 00:05:48,399
What's there to be afraid of?

89
00:05:49,120 --> 00:05:50,480
Ningxue, don't get it wrong.

90
00:05:50,759 --> 00:05:51,839
That's not what he meant.

91
00:05:52,240 --> 00:05:53,839
Everyone was getting a bit anxious.

92
00:05:55,040 --> 00:05:55,839
And,

93
00:05:56,439 --> 00:05:58,279
you know the company situation.

94
00:05:58,519 --> 00:05:59,360
As for Mr. Gu...

95
00:05:59,839 --> 00:06:01,800
So you're already calling him Mr. Gu?

96
00:06:02,800 --> 00:06:04,920
You're all eager to hand the Lin Group

97
00:06:05,399 --> 00:06:06,439
over to Gu Yuanbing, right?

98
00:06:07,120 --> 00:06:07,920
Lin Ningxue,

99
00:06:08,360 --> 00:06:09,600
mind your manners.

100
00:06:10,120 --> 00:06:12,480
Ever since Mr. Lin handed
the company to you,

101
00:06:12,560 --> 00:06:13,920
how much has the stock dropped?

102
00:06:14,800 --> 00:06:16,399
How much business has been lost?

103
00:06:17,279 --> 00:06:19,600
Only cooperation with the Gu Group

104
00:06:19,920 --> 00:06:21,480
is the best option now.

105
00:06:24,000 --> 00:06:25,439
Your so-called "best option"

106
00:06:25,639 --> 00:06:26,879
is just ignoring Gu's ambition

107
00:06:26,879 --> 00:06:29,040
to swallow the Lin Group whole.

108
00:06:30,160 --> 00:06:32,240
What exactly did Gu Yuanbing give you

109
00:06:32,240 --> 00:06:33,639
that made you betray the company?

110
00:06:35,199 --> 00:06:37,000
That's not how you put it.

111
00:06:37,600 --> 00:06:39,920
In business, there are
no permanent enemies,

112
00:06:40,199 --> 00:06:41,839
but permanent interests.

113
00:06:42,800 --> 00:06:44,839
We're thinking about
the company's interests,

114
00:06:45,199 --> 00:06:47,639
not the feud between
the Lin and Gu families.

115
00:06:48,519 --> 00:06:49,000
Exactly.

116
00:06:49,639 --> 00:06:50,439
Feud?

117
00:06:52,600 --> 00:06:55,199
What Gu wants is
our family's secret formula.

118
00:06:55,319 --> 00:06:57,319
He wants to ruin the whole Lin family.

119
00:06:57,360 --> 00:06:59,920
Are you all really unaware of this,
or just pretending?

120
00:07:01,399 --> 00:07:02,800
What does your feud with the Gu family

121
00:07:03,439 --> 00:07:04,879
have to do with us?

122
00:07:05,360 --> 00:07:07,240
The company isn't yours alone.

123
00:07:07,839 --> 00:07:09,160
Exactly.

124
00:07:10,399 --> 00:07:11,319
Ningxue,

125
00:07:11,839 --> 00:07:13,399
business is a battlefield.

126
00:07:14,480 --> 00:07:16,720
The situation overrides personal gain.

127
00:07:17,879 --> 00:07:18,839
Gu Yuanbing

128
00:07:19,560 --> 00:07:20,519
plays dirty.

129
00:07:21,160 --> 00:07:22,920
We've already lost too much.

130
00:07:23,720 --> 00:07:24,800
If we keep resisting,

131
00:07:25,319 --> 00:07:25,959
we...

132
00:07:28,720 --> 00:07:29,959
can't afford to lose.

133
00:07:31,000 --> 00:07:32,519
That's about you, not me.

134
00:07:32,959 --> 00:07:34,680
The Lin family still has backbone.

135
00:07:35,959 --> 00:07:37,600
My dad founded the Lin Group

136
00:07:37,680 --> 00:07:39,519
and never once thought
of yielding to the Gu family.

137
00:07:40,240 --> 00:07:41,720
If we say yes to the Gu family,

138
00:07:42,199 --> 00:07:43,920
tomorrow every single person here

139
00:07:43,920 --> 00:07:46,319
will be at their mercy!

140
00:07:46,639 --> 00:07:47,160
Enough!

141
00:07:47,959 --> 00:07:49,600
Stop fearmongering.

142
00:07:50,319 --> 00:07:52,439
Board votes are the rule.

143
00:07:53,720 --> 00:07:56,800
Those in favor of cooperation with
the Gu Group... raise your hands.

144
00:08:03,720 --> 00:08:04,519
Lin Ningxue,

145
00:08:05,560 --> 00:08:07,600
a wise man knows when to bend.

146
00:08:07,959 --> 00:08:08,800
Take my advice.

147
00:08:10,800 --> 00:08:13,480
Before my dad fell seriously ill,
he made it very clear:

148
00:08:14,120 --> 00:08:17,199
when he can no longer serve as chairman,

149
00:08:17,879 --> 00:08:20,399
all shares and decision-making power

150
00:08:20,399 --> 00:08:21,920
are to be fully entrusted to me.

151
00:08:22,680 --> 00:08:23,279
I

152
00:08:24,199 --> 00:08:25,759
have the right of veto.

153
00:08:27,279 --> 00:08:28,399
Still being stubborn!

154
00:08:29,000 --> 00:08:30,920
The group will be ruined by you!

155
00:08:35,279 --> 00:08:36,159
Wait and see.

156
00:09:37,240 --> 00:09:38,840
This Heavenly Yin Cold Marrow

157
00:09:40,399 --> 00:09:42,879
really can open
a mortal body's meridians

158
00:09:43,840 --> 00:09:44,879
and connect spiritual power.

159
00:09:48,759 --> 00:09:49,919
How is the company doing?

160
00:09:51,000 --> 00:09:53,440
The company... everything is fine.

161
00:09:55,200 --> 00:09:57,240
You've been strong-willed
since childhood.

162
00:09:57,519 --> 00:09:59,240
Your worries always show on your face.

163
00:10:00,240 --> 00:10:02,240
Did the Gu family try something else?

164
00:10:04,639 --> 00:10:07,440
All our previous partners are afraid
of the Gu family.

165
00:10:07,480 --> 00:10:08,919
They're cancelling contracts one by one.

166
00:10:09,480 --> 00:10:10,759
At this rate,

167
00:10:10,759 --> 00:10:11,799
in less than three months,

168
00:10:11,799 --> 00:10:14,120
the whole market's gonna be Gu family's.

169
00:10:15,279 --> 00:10:16,639
And the board...

170
00:10:17,559 --> 00:10:18,360
they...

171
00:10:19,559 --> 00:10:23,120
The Gu family is going
to wipe us out completely.

172
00:10:24,480 --> 00:10:24,879
Dad,

173
00:10:25,679 --> 00:10:26,679
as long as I'm here,

174
00:10:26,960 --> 00:10:29,320
I will never let Gu Yuanbing
get his way.

175
00:10:31,879 --> 00:10:32,840
At this point,

176
00:10:33,120 --> 00:10:35,080
only one person can save our family.

177
00:10:37,320 --> 00:10:38,240
You mean...?

178
00:10:39,320 --> 00:10:40,120
Su Wubing?

179
00:10:41,679 --> 00:10:42,720
I can tell...

180
00:10:43,080 --> 00:10:44,200
he's here for you.

181
00:10:51,519 --> 00:10:51,879
Mr. Lin,

182
00:10:51,879 --> 00:10:52,399
Miss,

183
00:10:52,399 --> 00:10:53,120
something's wrong!

184
00:10:53,120 --> 00:10:54,080
People from the Gu Group...

185
00:10:54,080 --> 00:10:54,559
What happened?

186
00:10:55,639 --> 00:10:57,279
Gu Yuanbing has forced his way in!

187
00:10:59,120 --> 00:11:00,279
Let's go!

188
00:11:13,159 --> 00:11:13,720
Rong.

189
00:11:14,320 --> 00:11:16,519
Mr. Gu is here in person today.

190
00:11:18,000 --> 00:11:19,559
We're not receiving guests today.

191
00:11:19,879 --> 00:11:20,600
Please leave.

192
00:11:23,840 --> 00:11:24,840
Mr. Lin,

193
00:11:25,559 --> 00:11:27,000
you've been unconscious for so long.

194
00:11:27,639 --> 00:11:29,399
Are you sure you understand
what's going on?

195
00:11:30,399 --> 00:11:31,840
My engagement with Lin Ningxue

196
00:11:32,480 --> 00:11:34,200
was something you begged for.

197
00:11:35,399 --> 00:11:37,279
And now you want to back out?

198
00:11:38,480 --> 00:11:39,840
You're embarassing Gu family?

199
00:11:41,559 --> 00:11:42,440
Mr. Gu,

200
00:11:42,480 --> 00:11:44,799
you're here to settle
the engagement, right?

201
00:11:45,080 --> 00:11:46,440
Now that Rong has recovered,

202
00:11:46,759 --> 00:11:48,120
let's just hold another wedding.

203
00:11:48,600 --> 00:11:50,120
Then it's settled.

204
00:11:52,440 --> 00:11:53,480
That's best.

205
00:11:54,679 --> 00:11:57,600
Otherwise it'll hurt
the Lin family's reputation.

206
00:11:59,200 --> 00:12:00,000
Gu Yuanbing,

207
00:12:00,159 --> 00:12:02,440
you used my dad's illness
to threaten me,

208
00:12:03,039 --> 00:12:05,240
so I had to agree to marry you.

209
00:12:07,960 --> 00:12:08,840
I came here today

210
00:12:09,639 --> 00:12:11,000
to show you some respect.

211
00:12:12,279 --> 00:12:13,679
You will marry me

212
00:12:14,200 --> 00:12:15,399
whether you want to or not!

213
00:12:21,639 --> 00:12:22,679
In Fan City,

214
00:12:24,080 --> 00:12:25,320
(Jiang Yao, Gu Group)
Mr. Gu's words

215
00:12:25,720 --> 00:12:27,000
(Jiang Yao, Gu Group)
are basically law.

216
00:12:30,879 --> 00:12:32,000
Who would dare disobey?

217
00:12:41,039 --> 00:12:41,840
See them out.

218
00:12:44,039 --> 00:12:44,840
Rong,

219
00:12:45,519 --> 00:12:47,639
we should put the family first.

220
00:12:49,120 --> 00:12:49,919
Lin Rong,

221
00:12:51,240 --> 00:12:53,240
I call you "sir" out of respect.

222
00:12:54,000 --> 00:12:54,840
Otherwise,

223
00:12:56,039 --> 00:12:57,799
you mean nothing to me.

224
00:12:57,799 --> 00:12:58,440
You...

225
00:13:00,320 --> 00:13:00,720
Dad!

226
00:13:01,600 --> 00:13:02,000
Dad...

227
00:13:05,840 --> 00:13:07,679
Gu Yuanbing, you're not welcome here.

228
00:13:08,919 --> 00:13:09,720
Ningxue,

229
00:13:10,240 --> 00:13:11,440
don't tell me you really think

230
00:13:11,440 --> 00:13:13,519
that Su guy can save you again.

231
00:13:17,320 --> 00:13:18,639
Come back with me obediently.

232
00:13:19,559 --> 00:13:20,399
Otherwise...

233
00:13:22,759 --> 00:13:23,320
Mr. Gu.

234
00:13:24,720 --> 00:13:25,919
You're pushing your luck.

235
00:13:25,919 --> 00:13:26,440
Stop it!

236
00:13:53,608 --> 00:13:57,711
♪I defy heaven, fate,
and so-called immortality♪

237
00:13:57,711 --> 00:14:02,431
♪At last you say
we've been apart too long♪

238
00:14:02,431 --> 00:14:07,311
♪Unwilling, unyielding, I won't let go♪

239
00:14:07,311 --> 00:14:12,431
♪With you, even a dried sea
learns to embrace a stream♪

240
00:14:12,431 --> 00:14:16,831
♪If heaven divides us, I'll reunite us,
with love as our vessel♪

241
00:14:16,831 --> 00:14:21,511
♪If it forbids it, I'll shatter
the absurd Heavenly Dao♪

242
00:14:21,511 --> 00:14:26,911
♪Even if countless stars
turn into my foes♪

243
00:14:26,911 --> 00:14:33,305
♪To grow old with you, we burn
through the end of the long night♪

